It becomes impossible to manage.
---------
Problem 3: What If Your System Crashes?

Very important question.
What if:
your laptop crashes?
your hard disk fails?
All your project files are gone.
This is a real risk.
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Git Solves All These Problems

This is where Git comes into the picture.

Git helps us to:
manage code properly
track every change
work with teams easily
keep backup safely
maintain complete history
-------
Git + Remote Repository

With Git, we usually use an online repository.
This repository:
stores your code safely
keeps a record of every change
has timestamps
has messages explaining why a change was made
So even if your system crashes,
your code is safe online.

-----------

Code Synchronization Made Easy

When you make changes:
