-----------

Going Back in Time (Very Powerful)

If a new feature breaks something:
you donâ€™t delete code
you donâ€™t rewrite everything
You just tell Git:
â€œTake me back to the previous versionâ€

Thatâ€™s it.
This works for every team member.
--------

Git History

Each time you submit code:

