Local System vs Online System

There are two places involved:

Local system
your laptop or computer
Online system
an online repository
also called a remote repository
A repository simply means:
ğŸ‘‰ a container that stores your project files and history
-------
Git vs GitHub (Very Important)

Remember this clearly:
Git â†’ tool that tracks changes
GitHub â†’ service that stores code online
GitHub is just a provider.
Other providers:
GitLab
Bitbucket
Concept remains the same everywhere.

------------------

Where We Actually Work (Working Directory)

On your system:
