--------------------

step-by-Step Git Lifecycle

The Git lifecycle works like this:

1ï¸Working Directory
2ï¸Staging Area
3ï¸Local Repository
4ï¸Online Repository (optional)

-------------
Git Add â†’ Staging Area

When we run:
